{
  "stem": "19111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to crawl on all-- on my belly and get through the line where the German watchmen, the, the police or the, the soldiers were watching, and reach that spot where that was and still, so-- very quietly, open it up and remove a piece of bread or a lump of sugar or, or, or a piece of cheese, and put it back together, so it wouldn't be recognized somehow.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did that quite a-- quite a number of times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were others that wanted to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they were actually brought to camp and given 25 lashes in front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as a youngster, I don't know, the rationale did not exist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew that it was risky in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it didn't enter my mind the, the enormous chances that I took, that all I wanted to do was get hold of that little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that went on for, for about five months like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after-- here, I must also mention that when we used to come back from work in the evening, the German who was in charge over there, he stood there, singing marches, so that everybody marched to his tune.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He enjoyed the fact that he was able to stand there and with his-- both arms, singing a march, some kind of a German march.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they sent us from there-- the-- at one point, after five months in this Camp Number I, they had a roll call.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought in some high-echelon Nazis-- Gestapo, doctors-- that were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
